    <item>
      <title>迁移博客使用Hexo搭建流程纪录</title>
      <link>https://lightlin.work//blog/2018/05/Hexo-Next-Blog.html</link>
      <guid>https://lightlin.work//blog/2018/05/Hexo-Next-Blog.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 May 2018 08:00:22 GMT</pubDate>
      <description>
      
        
        
          &lt;h2 id=&quot;博客主要第三方功能介绍&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#博客主要第三方功能介绍&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;博客主要第三方功能介绍&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;博客主要第三方功能介绍&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1,使用Hexo+Next主题搭建，Git
        
      
      </description>
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 id="博客主要第三方功能介绍"><a href="#博客主要第三方功能介绍" class="headerlink" title="博客主要第三方功能介绍"></a>博客主要第三方功能介绍</h2><blockquote><p>1,使用Hexo+Next主题搭建，GitHub托管，因此本来就包含的功能就不介绍了</p><p>2，网易云音乐插件</p><p>2，站内搜索localsearch</p><p>3，第三方评论系统：<a href="https://livere.com来必力" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://livere.com来必力</a></p><p>4，即时聊天插件： <a href="http://daovoice.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://daovoice.io/</a> DaoVoice</p><p>5，博客文章次数统计：<a href="https://leancloud.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://leancloud.cn/</a> Leancloud</p><p>6，博客被百度，Google收录步骤介绍</p><p>7，添加站内看板娘</p></blockquote><p>##博客所安装的Hexo—Next插件介绍</p><blockquote><p>1,站内搜索插件：hexo-generator-search和hexo-generator-searchdb</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> npm install hexo-generator-search --save</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> npm install hexo-generator-searchdb --save</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><blockquote><p>2,安装数字统计插件两个版本</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> npm i --save hexo-wordcount</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> //node在7.6.0之前安装</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> npm install hexo-wordcount@2 --save</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><blockquote></blockquote><h2 id="博客一些常用命令介绍"><a href="#博客一些常用命令介绍" class="headerlink" title="博客一些常用命令介绍"></a>博客一些常用命令介绍</h2><blockquote><p>安装与卸载插件</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> hexo安装xxx插件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> npm install xxx –save</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> hexo卸载xxx插件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> npm uninstall xxx</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><blockquote><p>清除缓存（已生成的静态文件）,编译生成，上传</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> hexo clean //清除</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> hexo g //生成</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> hexo d //上传</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><blockquote><p>注：区分主题配置文件_config.xml位于跟目录 和站点配置文件：_config.xml位于主题根目录</p></blockquote><h2 id="开始搭建Hexo-Next主题博客"><a href="#开始搭建Hexo-Next主题博客" class="headerlink" title="开始搭建Hexo+Next主题博客"></a>开始搭建Hexo+Next主题博客</h2><h3 id="基本博客生成步骤如下"><a href="#基本博客生成步骤如下" class="headerlink" title="基本博客生成步骤如下"></a>基本博客生成步骤如下</h3><blockquote><p>1，</p></blockquote><h3 id="增加站内搜索"><a href="#增加站内搜索" class="headerlink" title="增加站内搜索"></a>增加站内搜索</h3><blockquote><p> 1，next主题中自带三个搜索配置文件，由于第三方开始收费所以本站用的是Localsearch</p><p> 2，安装两个插件</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> npm install hexo-generator-search --save</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> npm install hexo-generator-searchdb --save</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><blockquote><p>3，编辑站点配置文件：_config.yml 添加如下配置。    ps：一般在跟目录</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> <span class="comment"># 添加搜索 field:post帖子，page页面，all所有</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> search:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash">   path: search.xml</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash">   field: post</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash">   format: html</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash">   <span class="built_in">limit</span>: 10000</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><blockquote><p>4，成功后会自动生成search.xml文件，其中以标签的形式收录了博客内容和跳转URL链接，可以在此检测下链接是否生成正确完整的访问路径。一般URL跳转错误都是此类问题导致。</p><p>注：若是生成有问题，自行编辑localsearch.swig文件，位置：themes\next\layout_scripts\third-party下。本博客源码已做修改，可以参考一下</p><p>本博客问题代码修改前如下：</p><figure class="highlight arduino"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; url: $( <span class="string">"url"</span> , <span class="keyword">this</span>).<span class="built_in">text</span>() <span class="comment">//源码已失效</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt; url: <span class="string">"&#123;&#123; config.url &#125;&#125;"</span>+$( <span class="string">"url"</span> , <span class="keyword">this</span>).<span class="built_in">text</span>()  <span class="comment">//修改后生效</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><blockquote></blockquote><h3 id="添加文字字数统计和阅读时长功能"><a href="#添加文字字数统计和阅读时长功能" class="headerlink" title="添加文字字数统计和阅读时长功能"></a>添加文字字数统计和阅读时长功能</h3><blockquote><p>1,因为Next主题默认集成了这功能所以我们只要检查下主题配置文件_config.xml是否开启以下配置：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> <span class="comment"># Post wordcount display settings</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> <span class="comment"># Dependencies: https://github.com/willin/hexo-wordcount</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> post_wordcount:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash">   item_text: <span class="literal">true</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash">   wordcount: <span class="literal">true</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash">   min2read: <span class="literal">true</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash">   totalcount: <span class="literal">true</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash">   separated_meta: <span class="literal">true</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><blockquote><p>2，若不显示还需要安装插件：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> npm i --save hexo-wordcount</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> //Node.js 7.6之前安装如下</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> npm install hexo-wordcount@2 --save</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><blockquote><p>参考链接：<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/baea8c95e39b" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.jianshu.com/p/baea8c95e39b</a></p></blockquote><h3 id="添加第三方评论系统来必力"><a href="#添加第三方评论系统来必力" class="headerlink" title="添加第三方评论系统来必力"></a>添加第三方评论系统来必力</h3><blockquote><p>1，注册来必力：<a href="https://livere.com具体我就不多说了" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://livere.com具体我就不多说了</a></p><p>2，点击右上角的头像选择进入管理页面 —》代码管理 —-》一般网站</p><img src="http://lightliin.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/18-6-2/7289549.jpg" width="600" height="200"><p>复制以上代码中的js文件路径替换themes\next\layout_scripts\third-party\comments目录下的livere.swig内容</p><p>3，并把主题配置_config.xml的livere_uid：的值配置成自己的</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> livere_uid: 你的ID（上图已标注）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><blockquote></blockquote><h3 id="添加即时通讯功能（与微信小程序绑定）"><a href="#添加即时通讯功能（与微信小程序绑定）" class="headerlink" title="添加即时通讯功能（与微信小程序绑定）"></a>添加即时通讯功能（与微信小程序绑定）</h3><blockquote><p>1，注册 <a href="http://daovoice.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://daovoice.io/</a>  DaoVoice具体不多说了。注：其中填写的企业名称就是今后你联系栏的名称，注册的名称就是其中一个接待用户。</p><p>2，参考下图，根据需要复制相应的代码，配置_config.xml下的app_id值</p><img src="http://lightliin.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/18-6-2/62926332.jpg" width="600" height="200"><p> 列:配置ID</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> <span class="comment"># Online contact</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> daovoice:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash">     <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash">     app_id: <span class="string">"id"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><blockquote><p>配置head.swig文件放在最后就行 路径：\themes\next\layout_partials</p><figure class="highlight django"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="xml">&gt; </span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name"><span class="name">if</span></span> theme.daovoice %&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">&gt;   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript">(<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params">i,s,o,g,r,a,m</span>)</span>&#123;i[<span class="string">"DaoVoiceObject"</span>]=r;i[r]=i[r]||<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span>&#123;(i[r].q=i[r].q||[]).push(<span class="built_in">arguments</span>)&#125;,i[r].l=<span class="number">1</span>*<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Date</span>();a=s.createElement(o),m=s.getElementsByTagName(o)[<span class="number">0</span>];a.async=<span class="number">1</span>;a.src=g;a.charset=<span class="string">"utf-8"</span>;m.parentNode.insertBefore(a,m)&#125;)(<span class="built_in">window</span>,<span class="built_in">document</span>,<span class="string">"script"</span>,(<span class="string">'https:'</span> == <span class="built_in">document</span>.location.protocol ? <span class="string">'https:'</span> : <span class="string">'http:'</span>) + <span class="string">"//widget.daovoice.io/widget/328973e7.js"</span>,<span class="string">"daovoice"</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">&gt;   daovoice('init', &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">&gt;       app_id: "</span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123; theme.daovoice.app_id &#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml">"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">&gt;     &#125;);</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">&gt;   daovoice('update');</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">&gt;   <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">&gt; </span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name"><span class="name">endif</span></span> %&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><blockquote><p>3，微信小程序绑定：点击官网控制台页面右上角用户，下拉菜单选择微信绑定，根据说明操作就行。</p></blockquote><h3 id="为文章添加阅读次数"><a href="#为文章添加阅读次数" class="headerlink" title="为文章添加阅读次数"></a>为文章添加阅读次数</h3><blockquote><p>1,注册<a href="https://leancloud.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://leancloud.cn/</a> Leancloud账号</p><p>2，创建应用，取名字等，然后点击存储——》点击创建Class——》取名“Counter”——》权限选择无限制—-》创建成功</p><img src="http://lightliin.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/18-6-5/9015998.jpg" width="undefined" height="undefined"><img src="http://lightliin.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/18-6-5/8875530.jpg" width="undefined" height="undefined"><p>根据上图做好相应操作即可。</p><p>3,在主题配置_config.xml下找到并配置如下代码</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> <span class="comment"># Show number of visitors to each article.</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> <span class="comment"># You can visit https://leancloud.cn get AppID and AppKey.</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> leancloud_visitors:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash">   <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash">   app_id: 你的ID</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash">   app_key: 你的key</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><blockquote><p>注：因为本hexo_Next主题自带了阅读次数配置与模板，所以只需创建好名字为：“Counter”的存储表以及自己的ID与key就行；</p><p>其余请参考：<a href="http://www.jeyzhang.com/hexo-next-add-post-views.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://www.jeyzhang.com/hexo-next-add-post-views.html</a></p></blockquote>]]></content:encoded>
      
